Alembic migrations, async.

- Apply all:           alembic upgrade head          (or: make migrate)
- Roll back one:       alembic downgrade -1          (or: make migrate-down)
- Autogenerate new:    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "message"
                                                     (or: make migrate-create msg="message")

env.py pulls the DB URL from `app.config.settings`, so no credentials
live in alembic.ini.
